# Classroom Attendance DApp

A decentralized application (DApp) built using Scaffold-ETH 2 for managing classroom attendance on the blockchain.

## Features
- Create attendance sessions
- Record student attendance (Present/Absent)
- Store student name, teacher, and module details
- View attendance records

## Tech Stack
- Solidity (Smart Contracts)
- Hardhat
- Next.js (Frontend)
- Scaffold-ETH 2
- Ethers.js

## How to Run

```bash
yarn install
yarn start
yarn deploy
